outputs.output_descr:
NAYCOM and MYES capacitated in leading and coordinating youth policy and programmes in the country
Increased youth employment through career advice and job placement services, internship programmes and business development services
Indigenous youth-led initiatives are more effectively managed
SABI centre improved to provide the required research, training and agro technology for increased productivity and youth employment

project_descr: Youth Employment and Empowerment by enhancing Government and UN interventions in reducing unemployment among youth in Sierra Leone and in consolidating the peace building efforts.
